[SN]TITLE[SN]
Rio Olympics 2016: Australia smash women's 4x100m freestyle relay world record

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Australia won a second Olympic swimming gold medal on the opening day of Rio 2016 by setting a world record in the women's 4x100m freestyle relay.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
